      "text": "This is why (uniquely for me) my thoughts and phosphene activity speeded up in March so that the rate was beyond count. My personal time used itself up...but for me the actual Fulfillment of Time wsa quite different from the Day of Wrath under acid in 1964, ten years or so earlier. I saw the Day of Judgment this time, when it wsa real, only that Sunday night when the pale white light filled the room and I once more knew death was there, and began to pray frantically in Latin, exactly as I had do",
